data.description: Charming historical home across from Central Park in Carthage!  Featuring over 2500 SF on 2 levels, this move-in ready home offers 4 beds, 2 baths, a pantry, covered front porch, and detached garage!  Inside, discover hardwood floors in the front dining room, and a living room with fireplace and pocket doors to a den/2nd dining area.  The spacious kitchen features wood cabinets, a pantry, storage closet, and exterior access to the side of the house.  The main floor is completed by a large bedroom and full bathroom with walk-in tiled shower.  Upstairs, 3 more sizable bedrooms share a full hall bathroom and large laundry room!  Off the kitchen is 2nd covered side patio with stairs down to the detached garage. Enjoy Food Truck Friday at Central Park and the nearby conveniences of Garrison and Central Avenue!  Call to schedule a tour today!
